OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780207510
OL,3,CFirst of five men trapped in flooded
OL,4,CLaos cave evacuated by rescue team
OL,6,FThe first of five villagers trapped in
OL,7,Fa flooded cave in Laos for more than a
OL,8,Fweek has been safely evacuated by
OL,9,Frescue workers.
OL,11,FFootage shared by Lao and Thai rescue
OL,12,Fservices showed a man unsteadily being
OL,13,Fescorted out of the cave in Laos'
OL,14,Fcentral Xaisomboun province with a
OL,15,Ftorch strapped to his forehead late on
OL,16,FFriday evening local time.
OL,18,FHe was then handed over to other
OL,19,Fmembers of the rescue team for a
OL,20,Fmedical check as a crowd of people
OL,21,Fwatched on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
