OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780207510
OL,3,CFirst of five men trapped in flooded
OL,4,CLaos cave evacuated by rescue team
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FFive of seven people trapped inside
OL,12,Fthe underground cavern were found by
OL,13,Fdivers on Wednesday, with the other
OL,14,Ftwo still missing as of Friday.
OL,16,FThe five have been identified by their
OL,17,Ffirst names as Khamla, Mued, Ee, Ing,
OL,18,Fand Laen, and were reportedly found in
OL,19,Fgood health but exhausted from
OL,20,Fdehydration and lack of food.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780207510
OL,3,CFirst of five men trapped in flooded
OL,4,CLaos cave evacuated by rescue team
OL,6,FIt is not clear which of them was
OL,7,Fevacuated first, but the four
OL,8,Fremaining have been supplied with
OL,9,Fwater, soft food, and foil blankets to
OL,10,Fkeep them warm.
OL,12,FTheir evacuations have been suspended
OL,13,Funtil Saturday as they were not ready,
OL,14,Fsaid Chakkit Taengtang of Sai Than
OL,15,FAssociation, one of the Thai rescue
OL,16,Forganisations at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
