PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780207510
OL,3,CFirst of five men trapped in flooded
OL,4,CLaos cave evacuated by rescue team
OL,6,FIn a video shot inside the cave on
OL,7,FThursday, villager Khamla could be
OL,8,Fheard telling Thai rescue diver
OL,9,FNorrased Palasing: "I can't go on. I
OL,10,Fdon't have any strength."
OL,12,FAnother villager Mued also delivered a
OL,13,Fmessage to his family, telling them:
OL,14,F"Don't worry mom, dad. I'm still
OL,15,Fstrong, I'm still healthy. Tomorrow I
OL,16,Fwill be home. I love you, mom and dad."
OL,18,FRescue teams pumped water out of the
OL,19,Fflooded cave's passages on Friday, but
OL,20,Fa morning rainstorm complicated their
OL,21,Fwork.
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@gO]
