PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780207510
OL,3,CFirst of five men trapped in flooded
OL,4,CLaos cave evacuated by rescue team
OL,6,FThe villagers had reportedly entered
OL,7,Fthe cave last week to look for
OL,8,Fvaluable minerals before being trapped
OL,9,Fby flash flooding that blocked their
OL,10,Fway out.
OL,12,FOne other villager escaped in time and
OL,13,Falerted the authorities to the seven
OL,14,Fleft behind.
OL,16,FRescue teams from Laos and neighboring
OL,17,FThailand have been joined by Japanese
OL,18,Fand Malaysian colleagues, with
OL,19,FIndonesian and French specialists
OL,20,Freported to be coming to help with the
OL,21,Foperation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
