PN,31806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780207510
OL,3,CFirst of five men trapped in flooded
OL,4,CLaos cave evacuated by rescue team
OL,6,FTo find the villagers, divers had to
OL,7,Fmake their way through twisting,
OL,8,Fnarrow, flooded passages with jagged
OL,9,Fwalls in the dark.
OL,11,FThe experts have had to weigh the
OL,12,Frisks of guiding survivors with no
OL,13,Fdiving skills through zero-visibility
OL,14,Fwater against the strategy of waiting
OL,15,Ffor water levels to recede, said Gary
OL,16,FMitchell, who took part in the rescue
OL,17,Fof 12 schoolboys from a cave in
OL,18,FThailand in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
