PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1780207510
OL,3,CFirst of five men trapped in flooded
OL,4,CLaos cave evacuated by rescue team
OL,6,F"You can't leave people underground
OL,7,Ftoo long without medical support,
OL,8,Fwithout proper food, sustenance, clean
OL,9,Fwater ... before their condition is
OL,10,Fgoing to deteriorate," Mitchell, press
OL,11,Fofficer for the South and Mid Wales
OL,12,FCave Rescue Team, told AP.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
